Document: VisualShaderNodeIntParameter
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeintparameter.rst
Summary: Defines an integer parameter node for Visual Shaders with range customization.
VisualShaderNodeIntParameter is a VisualShaderNodeParameter of type int. It offers additional customization for the range of accepted values.
